OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and grey start to the
OL,6,Fday across the region. Some brighter
OL,7,Fspells are likely to develop, but a
OL,8,Ffew showers are possible too. Feeling
OL,9,Fpleasant in any brighter interludes.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers mostly fading during
OL,12,Fthe evening. Largely cloudy and dry
OL,13,Ftonight, although a slight chance of
OL,14,Fthe odd shower where the cloud
OL,15,Fthickens. Staying fairly mild.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FCloudy skies at first,
OL,18,Fperhaps with the odd shower. Drier in
OL,19,Fthe afternoon with some brighter
OL,20,Fglimmers developing. Feeling fresher.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
